<div class="w-100 bg-white center pa3 mb5 f4">
  <div class="mv4 flex center w5-1">
    <p class="mv2">
      <%= emoji_img_tag(static_path(@conn, src_image(@emotion)), class: "w-25 fl") %>
      Sometimes it's hard to know what it is that you're feeling. But often,
      our bodies can give us helpful clues.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="mv4 flex center w5-1">
    <p>
      I recommend you try to describe how you’re feeling, and send this
      information to someone. That way they can help you understand this better.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="">
    <%= custom_render_autoform(
      @conn,
      :create,
      [
        "<div class=\"form-group-reason mt4 w-90 center\">",
        {
          @module,
          custom_labels: %{reason: "Say it in your own words"},
          exclude: Emotion.reason_list() ++ [:feeling]
        },
        "</div>",
      ],
      assigns: [changeset: @changeset])
    %>
  </div>

  <div class="mv4 center tc lh-title">
    <p class="mb2">
      If you can’t wait for someone to read your email, you can call Childline
      to talk to someone right now.</p>
    <p class="b afc-red">Call Childline on 0800 1111</p>
  </div>
</div>
